{"id":352552,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/06/【图说天朝】动真格：反恐维稳一锅端/","date":"2014-07-01T06:20:47Z","modified":"2015-12-10T01:26:49Z","title":"【图说天朝】动真格：反恐维稳一锅端","content":"<p>来源：<a href=\"http://weibo.com/nddaily\">@南方都市报</a></p>\n<blockquote><p>@南方都市报：#南都快讯#【江门公安反恐演练动真格 警盾被砖头砸烂 有民警受伤】煤气瓶、燃烧弹、震爆弹、催泪弹、满天飞的砖头&#8230;&#8230;今日上午，广东江门公安举行反恐处突演练，模拟“毒疯子”持煤气瓶自杀、恐怖分子袭击城轨车站，现场“道具”都是真家伙，警盾还被砖头砸烂，有民警因此受伤。记者曾育军 孙振飞</p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/04/%E3%80%90%E5%9B%BE%E8%AF%B4%E5%A4%A9%E6%9C%9D%E3%80%91%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E4%B8%BA%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91/\">【图说天朝】与人民群众打成一片</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/04/%E3%80%90%E5%9B%BE%E8%AF%B4%E5%A4%A9%E6%9C%9D%E3%80%91%E4%BA%AE%E5%89%91%E7%BB%83%E6%9E%AA%EF%BC%9A%E5%9B%9B%E5%B7%9D%E9%92%A2%E9%93%81%E4%BE%A0/\">【图说天朝】亮剑练枪：四川钢铁侠</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/06/6204ece1gw1ehw8lziy68j21kw11xws5.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-352553\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/06/6204ece1gw1ehw8lziy68j21kw11xws5.jpg\" alt=\"6204ece1gw1ehw8lziy68j21kw11xws5\" width=\"565\" height=\"376\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/06/6204ece1gw1ehw8lziy68j21kw11xws5.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/06/6204ece1gw1ehw8lziy68j21kw11xws5-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 565px) 100vw, 565px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/06/6204ece1gw1ehw8m0wm46j21kw11xqgb.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-352554\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/06/6204ece1gw1ehw8m0wm46j21kw11xqgb.jpg\" alt=\"6204ece1gw1ehw8m0wm46j21kw11xqgb\" width=\"565\" height=\"376\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/06/6204ece1gw1ehw8m0wm46j21kw11xqgb.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/06/6204ece1gw1ehw8m0wm46j21kw11xqgb-300x199.jpg 300w\" s